ActBusiness Development Bank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Small Business and Tourism of CATHY BENNETT of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Claude Mc Master, whose term has expired.
